{"tid":1885510,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日常負責採訪安倍晉三的記者被隔離","createTime":"2020-02-18T10:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:20:14.000Z","uid":35519,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60cda4a7ef971419a679b0ae1015db68752c0f6f","tid":1885510,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"提醒:本消息暫未獲得日本官方證實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原標題:<br />\n日本共同社10人隔離，其中1人為首相官邸採訪記者<br />\n <br />\n17日夜間，日本共同社報導稱，16日確診為新冠肺炎的司機曾在為共同社提供包車駕駛服務。在自1月底至2月初的4天中，共同社員工共有10人乘坐過該車。現時，10人均無發熱等症狀，他們也於17日起被要求在家隔離待命。據相關人士透露，10人中，有1人為共同社政治部承擔首相官邸採訪任務的記者。<br />\n <br />\n據日媒消息，相關人士透露，被隔離女記者日常負責採訪日本首相安倍晋三，同時也負責採訪秘書官。如傳染秘書官，也有風險可能傳染給首相。現時，出席記者會的人員均已開始戴口罩。<br />\n <br />\n消息來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://rn.mbd.baidu.com/9gs818s?f=cp&amp;u=e8d0406bf8e40e66\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frn.mbd.baidu.com%2F9gs818s%3Ff%3Dcp%26u%3De8d0406bf8e40e66&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=4797a64f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rn.mbd.baidu.com/9gs818s?f=cp&amp;u=e8d0406bf8e40e66</a><br />\n<br />\n[爆卦] 日常負責採訪安倍晉三的記者被隔離<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/ask/over18?from=%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1582021400.A.183.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fask%2Fover18%3Ffrom%3D%252Fbbs%252FGossiping%252FM.1582021400.A.183.html&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=1977f998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/ask/over18?from=%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1582021400.A.183.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff94c10ecd29cf46b609d095a8e7888fe67f0bcf","tid":1885510,"uid":273228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"日本rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b911e0498c26adb96ac58e83293d2118fe5311ff","tid":1885510,"uid":238415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"都無大流行...點解要隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.g